Speaker 1: All right, Frank, let's do some digging here. Can I get your date of birth so I can pull up your chart?

Speaker 2: 4-19-64.

Speaker 1: So, Frank, it looks like it is currently in the Kansas City Distribution Center.

Speaker 1: So then they'll get a text message on when it's going to be delivered?

Speaker 1: All right, bear with me here.

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 2: Is that what it says there?

Speaker 1: No, it doesn't say anything.

Speaker 2: It just gives me a tracking number.

Speaker 1: That's it.

Speaker 2: Okay, so if you click that, it'll show your status, and then you will get text messages on any updates for your shipment.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: That's the strange thing.

Speaker 2: Usually, USPS has a little bit more detail.

Speaker 1: It just says the item is in transit to the destination.
